description:
This video is brought to you by Nebula. Get a GREAT deal on Nebula now: https://go.nebula.tv/captainmidnight
Season 36 is not a very notable season of The Simpsons, but its interesting in how it feels like the show actively wants to end. In this video we go over the strange "Bart's Birthday" alongside the Christmas Special on Disney Plus.
